    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 22.82,
      "end": 23.66,
      "text": "ASop's Fables.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 24.26,
      "end": 25.02,
      "text": "The Image Seller.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 26.02,
      "end": 32.14,
      "text": "A certain man made a wooden image of moigery and exposed it for sale in the market.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 33.02,
      "end": 39.52,
      "text": "As no one offered to buy it, however, he thought he would try to attract a purchaser by proclaiming",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 39.52,
      "end": 41.5,
      "text": "the Foychus of the image.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 42.6,
      "end": 49.74,
      "text": "So, he cried up and down to market, a god for sale, a god for sale, one who bring you",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 49.74,
      "end": 51.72,
      "text": "luck and keep you lucky.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 53.46,
      "end": 59.3,
      "text": "Presently, one of the bystanders stopped him and said, If your god is all you make him",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-015",
      "start": 59.3,
      "end": 63.56,
      "text": "out to be, how is it you don't keep him and make the most of him yourself?",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-016",
      "start": 65.08,
      "end": 67.54,
      "text": "I'll tell you why, replied he.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-017",
      "start": 68.46,
      "end": 77.34,
      "text": "He brings gain, it is true, but he takes his time about it, whereas I want my money at",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-018",
      "start": 77.34,
      "end": 77.74,
      "text": "once.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-019",
      "start": 78.9,
      "end": 81.42,
      "text": "End of the image seller.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
